videos.description: Florida State's Mfiondu Kabengele capitalizes on a missed 3-pointer with a putback dunk and follows that play with a big-time block on defense.
videos.headline: FSU's Kabengele follows putback dunk with rejection at rim

videos.description: Florida State's Mfinodu Kabengele gets a dish at the rim and throws down a two-handed dunk with a foul.
videos.headline: FSU's Kabengele powers through contact for dunk

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Mitchell Solomon send backs the dunk attempt at the rim by Florida State's Phil Cofer.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Solomon rejects dunk attempt

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Tavarius Shine intercepts a pass and takes it the other way for the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State's Shine punctuates steal with dunk

videos.description: Florida State's CJ Walker hits Phil Cofer with a lob who throws down the dunk.
videos.headline: FSU connect on rim-rocking alley-oop

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Mitchell Solomon tips in the missed shot with a few seconds left to give the Cowboys a 71-70 win over Florida State.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State upsets Florida State with late tip-in
